# URLs to skip when checking for broken links.
# Add hosts here that are known-good but frequently return transient errors
# or block CI link checkers.

# Mozilla support occasionally returns 502 Bad Gateway
https://support.mozilla.org/.*

# Pinterest often 429/403s CI checkers
https://www.pinterest.com/.*

# GitHub raw source files and blob deep-links rate-limit aggressively from
# CI; they're in the al-folio template docs only.
https://github.com/alshedivat/al-folio/blob/.*
